      <hedline>
        <hl1>Alone at the Top</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Jack Siegrist letter on Roger Lowenstein's August 27 profile of Sanford I Weill holds that if he were cast on Survivor, he would win million dollars, CBS and all its affiliates (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>If Sandy Weill were cast on ''Survivor,'' he would win not only the million dollars but also CBS and all the affiliates.</p>
        <p>Jack Siegrist  Shrewsbury, N.J.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>If Sandy Weill were cast on ''Survivor,'' he would win not only the million dollars but also CBS and all the affiliates.</p>
